---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: España TSI Input
description: an input for entering a Tarjeta Sanitaria Individual (TSI) code
---

{% from "components/espana-tarjeta-sanitaria-individual-input/macro.njk" import espanaTarjetaSanitariaIndividualInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/hint/macro.njk" import hint %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Por defecto</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "tsi", text: "Tarjeta Sanitaria Individual" }) }}
  {{ hint({
    id: "tsi-hint",
    text: "Código alfanumérico. El formato depende de la comunidad autónoma."
  }) }}
  {{ espanaTarjetaSanitariaIndividualInput({
    id: "tsi",
    describedBy: "tsi-hint"
  }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format varies by region</h2>
<p>Each autonomous community issues its TSI with a different
  format. The input accepts up to 20 alphanumeric characters and
  does not impose auto-grouping — consumers apply region-specific
  validation as needed.</p>
